# Build artifacts left by the GUI/website packages' `build` scripts
# (ng build cache, devtool's `zip -r dist.zip dist`, desktop-ui's typedoc `docs.json`).
# These are emitted by `lerna run build` (a full `npm run build`) and otherwise show
# up as untracked junk — none of it is needed by consumers of the library packages.
.angular
packages/*/dist.zip
packages/desktop-ui/docs.json
*docs-json.d.ts
.typedoc-html

# Nx task-runner cache (build ordering + caching is configured in nx.json)
.nx/
